gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 106, Clippers 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Clippers, 106-103. LeBron James led the way for the Lakers with 25 points, eight rebounds and seven assists, while Anthony Davis added 22 points and 10 rebounds in the victory. Paul George (22 points, five steals) and Ivica Zubac (22 points, 19 rebounds) combined for 44 points for the Clippers in the losing effort. The Lakers snap a 4-game losing streak as they improve to 18-19 on the season, while the Clippers snap a 5-game winning streak as they fall to 22-13.
